snippet.title: Showdown of Fate Gameplay Android
snippet.description:
There are various types of beauty characters here, come and participate in our exciting game!
feature:
You can collect various beauty cards. You can upgrade them, then form a war party and go on an adventure!
1. Collect characters
We have a hundred kinds of beautiful characters with various shapes for you to pick.
2. Gear up your partner
Get abundant resources, then upgrade your team and go for the challenge!
3. Team work
Fighting side by side with your friends.
4. Multiple combat modes
Different types of enemies, you need to be flexible to deal with them!




Download:  
Apkcombo - https://apkcombo.com/showdown-of-fate/showdown.of.fate/
Play Market - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=showdown.of.fate
